557 to 551 West 169th Street, north side, east from a point midway between Broadway (also St. Nicholas Ave., at this point) and Audubon Ave., and to the latter (on the right), showing three frame houses, os. 557, 555 and 553. No. 551 is the 6-story apartment house at the N.W. corner of Audubon Ave. and upon which it bears No. 80.

July 30, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.
